name: Mogu
body:
### Welcome to mogu zone.
This automatic page generator is the easiest way to create beautiful pages for all of your projects. Author your page content here [using GitHub Flavored Markdown](http://user.qzone.qq.com/1463321578?ADUIN=522428231&ADSESSION=1466669227&ADTAG=CLIENT.QQ.5437_FriendTip.0&ADPUBNO=26517&ptlang=2052), select a template crafted by a designer, and publish. After your page is generated, you can check out the new `gh-pages` branch locally. If you’re using GitHub Desktop, simply sync your repository and you’ll see the new branch.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
